social_posts.post_text: The most patient dog. He protects my babies like none other. He’s just the best. Theo is pretty obsessed too.🥰🤍

Nora was shocked Charlie made the nice list.😆(like any little sister would think). Theo should be on the naughty list. Bernie was definitely top of the nice list. And Nora goes back and forth on the lists😜… this year was neat to watch them all experience the activities, very grateful for all we have been given. It’s been so special to serve others with the big girls this year. Trying to show them to keep in my mind what Christmas is truly about. Merry Christmas! #happybirthdayjesus🎁🎄 ⛪️

This just popped up on my account😂 I’m dying laughing, some people might remember this when we lived in Boston but a tree had fallen on our driveway and he thought he was gonna chop it up with this.😂😂😂 @gordonhayward

Nora Mae you’re 4! She is so smart, fearless, “spicy”, hilarious for a 4 year old. (You can definitely tell she’s the 3rd). She keeps us on our toes for sure. Nora has no problem telling anyone they’re wrong and has no problem being a snitch on her siblings. 😂 We couldn’t imagine her any other way, we love you Nora! Happy birthday!💕 @gordonhayward
Very grateful for all these boys.. they put up with a lot of girls everyday.🤍💕 @gordonhayward #happyvalentinesday

Maggie! I can’t believe you’re 16 today! You were my first baby from the day I met you. I’m so lucky God chose us to be sisters. You are the strongest, kindest, most giving girl I’ve known. Everything you’ve endured and still been able to be who you are is incredible. I will always admire you. I love you forever. You’re always my baby, but now we can be best friends too! Love you sweet girl! Happy 16th birthday! 💕🎊🎉
Happy Birthday to my best friend! We’re lucky to call you ours, you’re the best dad and husband we could ever wish for! Love you forever old man!😘 @gordonhayward

Bernie made her First Communion today. She wore the same dress I wore which is special, she was so excited to have my mom and Grandma there to watch her. It’s so neat to have a picture of 4 generations of our family.❤️

Happy 8th birthday Bernie girl! Celebrating you is so easy! You’re  the kindest, most thoughtful, brilliant, funny, and beautiful little girl. You make being your mom so easy. We are so lucky you are ours! The best sister and daughter we could ever ask for! Love you forever and always💕🎊🎉🎈

(The video of Bernie is my favorite, anyone who knew Bernie when she was little will remember her cute little raspy voice🥰)
Charlie I can’t believe you’re 7 years old! You are smart, spicy, kind, and beautiful! We love you so much!💕🎉🎈

My sweet boy is 3 today! You are ginormous and sweet, you are silly and love the attention of your sisters. We couldn’t imagine our life without you, you keep us on our toes being mischievous. We love you so much Theo 🩵 @gordonhayward
Siber you were the most loving, protective, and patient boy with all my babies. We were always safe with you. There will never be another you Bubbie. I love you forever 🩵
